name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Corona Hider - Block COVID-19 from the Web!

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Take a break from the pandemic when surfing the net.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With the overwhelming news of coronavirus everywhere we look; our phones, TV, friends and family, sometimes its nice to just take a break, especially for our mental health. It works on many websites; give it a shot and let me know of any feedback.
